<p>There is quite a bit of humor (especially dark humor), but any themes are really by accident based on our pretty eclectic tastes. There was never a plan. Almost everything we own was purchased within an hour of first seeing it.</p>
<div id="attachment_42827" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 600px">
	<a href="http://static.artfagcity.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/barry_james29s.jpeg"><img class="size-full wp-image-42827" title="barry_james29s" src="http://static.artfagcity.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/barry_james29s.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="400" /></a>
