	<li>According to artist and Occupy Wall Street activist Molly Crabapple?s Twitter feed she was arrested yesterday for standing on a sidewalk during an Occupy protest. Most recently, the artist was one of more than 20 artists CNN invited <a href="http://www.cnn.com/interactive/2012/08/opinion/power.gallery/index.html">to make work about the election</a>. Today, Crabapple was included in CNN?s slideshow of photographs documenting the OWS arrests. [<a href="http://www.cnn.com/2012/09/16/us/gallery/occupy-one-year/index.html">CNN</a>]</li>
